"```sql\nSELECT \n    (consumption_2012 - consumption_2013) / consumption_2012 AS consumption_decrease_rate\nFROM (\n    SELECT \n        SUM(CASE WHEN yearmonth.Date LIKE '2012%' THEN yearmonth.Consumption ELSE 0 END) AS consumption_2012,\n        SUM(CASE WHEN yearmonth.Date LIKE '2013%' THEN yearmonth.Consumption ELSE 0 END) AS consumption_2013\n    FROM yearmonth\n    WHERE yearmonth.CustomerID = (\n        SELECT transactions_1k.CustomerID\n        FROM transactions_1k\n        WHERE transactions_1k.Amount = 634.8 AND transactions_1k.Date = '2012-08-25'\n    )\n) AS consumption_data;\n```"